text: Forel-sur-Lucens is a former municipality of the district Broye-Vully in the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. On 1 January 2017, it is part of the municipality of Lucens.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Former municipalities of Vaud
